{"tid":1975204,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"火力全開 - 要求中國賠償香港武漢肺炎損失！","createTime":"2020-04-16T11:28:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-24T10:44:18.000Z","uid":235257,"like":41,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"baca65751507707e90f580f3e02fd4dd9e811976","tid":1975204,"uid":235257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T11:28:49.000Z","msg":"［聯署就快到Deadline］<br />\n美國已正式宣布cut世衛budget，已向親共的世衛打響第一炮，香港人要醒水識企美國個邊。幫簽以下聯署，表示Hong Kong is not China，希望美國能在大蕭條時多多關照香港。<br />\n<br />\n請求美國代香港人向中共追討因武漢病毒造成的損失聯署:<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-reparation-behalf-hong-kong-people-loss-due-chinese-virus\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frequest-reparation-behalf-hong-kong-people-loss-due-chinese-virus&d=74s%2FNZguDZpTF4W18ni10HKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=39e977c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-reparation-behalf-hong-kong-people-loss-due-chinese-virus</a><br />\n<br />\n聯署程序：簽署&gt;查電郵&gt;確定簽署&gt;廣傳<br />\n<br />\n#MakeChinaPay<br />\n#城邦行動派<br />\n#美軍未來我邀請 #美軍來了我帶路"},{"pid":"4d48e4401304c31203cf3eec964ed1aa9e564ba5","tid":1975204,"uid":235257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T11:28:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"634ecc98cb6ea0169350a4abf6a6cf1197568dfa","tid":1975204,"uid":235257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T11:29:44.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">求援美國 追殺中共</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"98ad0d5a5c5c84ec8207513b112029d7f6b57e67","tid":1975204,"uid":251328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T11:31:28.000Z","msg":"根本支那大撚把野要賠俾香港添"},{"pid":"84cf886e92904efc9f8da53e4aa56a8328fdb8c7","tid":1975204,"uid":235257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T11:31:40.000Z","msg":"全世界都要中共賠錢，香港人被共產黨害到雞毛鴨血，唔簽唔係人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40e678bef3c7515849283ccf673d8857c1b78378","tid":1975204,"uid":235257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98ad0d5a5c5c84ec8207513b112029d7f6b57e67","tid":1975204,"uid":251328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T11:31:28.000Z","msg":"根本支那大撚把野要賠俾香港添"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T11:32:54.000Z","msg":"無撚錯，搞到香港大把人失業一日個原因就係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">共產黨</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">共匪落地獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"74aed7f5e34a16aec67798d57d0f56d6b9824388","tid":1975204,"uid":235257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T11:35:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">今鋪真係要共黨死清光<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"fc003f82d42ac713856553d2a33f629af50d5347","tid":1975204,"uid":235257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T11:38:56.000Z","msg":"【香港經濟】華僑永亨：「最壞的情况仍未到」 料中短期破產個案上升<br />\n<br />\n 金融經濟 18:22 2020/04/16 <br />\n李若凡指出，指出，如果更多中小企業陷入困境，急需要現金流的中小企業主，可能會以很低的折扣價變賣其住宅物業套現。<br />\n<br />\n▲ 李若凡指出，指出，如果更多中小企業陷入困境，急需要現金流的中小企業主，可能會以很低的折扣價變賣其住宅物業套現。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎在全球大流行，重創環球經濟。華僑永亨銀行經濟師李若凡今發表報告，並以「最壞的情况仍未到」為題，指雖然政府現已推出一系列的刺激措施，但料不足以扭轉經濟下滑的情況，預計中短期的破產個案可能會上升。<br />\n<br />\n私人消費大受打擊<br />\n<br />\n李若凡指出，雖然政府現推出一系列的刺激措施，支持受影響的中小企業，但她認為，這些措施可能不足以扭轉本港經濟下滑的局面，尤其是在疫症大流行將持續更長時間的情况下。她以過去經濟衰退歷史作為參考，預計中短期的破產個案可能會增加。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n她指出，隨着就業機會減少及企業減薪壓力，再加上近期股市暴跌及社會隔離措施，均對財富效應造成負面影響，料將嚴重影響私人消費，加上外部需求疲弱，預計今年本港將出現更深的經濟萎縮，按年收縮2.1%。<br />\n<br />\n料樓價今年跌15%<br />\n<br />\n她指出，如果更多中小企業陷入困境，急需要現金流的中小企業主，可能會以很低的折扣價變賣其住宅物業套現。另方面，市場對裁員及減薪的擔憂可能會拖累買樓需求，預計今年樓價將按年下降15%。<br />\n<br />\n相關文章：<br />\n<br />\n【香港經濟】陳茂波：或進一步下調今年香港GDP預測<br />\n<br />\n中國首季GDP明出爐料首現負增長 一文看清市場預測<br />\n<br />\n免費下載 hket App，關注「全球疫情實時動態」<br />\n<br />\n一APP在手洞悉天下 立即訂閱送高達$480訂閱禮品<br />\n<br />\n編輯：吳敏芳"},{"pid":"dcdbecb7d52f5fc94dcc07f9cc4f4f5fc20d3a4d","tid":1975204,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T11:43:06.000Z","msg":"點解唔直接係香港告？"},{"pid":"e01250b0530dbe3914b28e5a775613e278a44a02","tid":1975204,"uid":235257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dcdbecb7d52f5fc94dcc07f9cc4f4f5fc20d3a4d","tid":1975204,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T11:43:06.000Z","msg":"點解唔直接係香港告？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T11:47:11.000Z","msg":"兩樣無衝突，可以雙管齊下"},{"pid":"c66219d1bf776a73d86cdeeed777a0e36eaf969c","tid":1975204,"uid":235257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T12:05:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">IN US WE TRUST</span></span>"},{"pid":"74b8182022f06cc3f235509035588f2712a3c934","tid":1975204,"uid":235257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T12:06:28.000Z","msg":"撇不開中共 活不了香港<br />\n<br />\n特朗普識破中共特務身分，很是高興。但中共的毒計不此於此。牠知道世界恨惡自己，更要世界憎恨香港。<br />\n<br />\n短短數小時，該影片就有近二萬點擊。全世界正認為香港就是中共問題的輸出點。看看台灣那邊的報道，十分中肯，沒有為香港澄清，全世界也沒有為香港澄清。外國人眼中，這事件顯示出香港媒體實為中共特務。簡單來說，就是「香港就是中共國」（Hong King is just China）！<br />\n<br />\n而現在被炒熱的中共病毒問題，你知道有多少是中共借香港轉口嗎？很多囉。尤其外國人眼見香港人的行徑，認定這裏是疫埠。被追究責任時，香港會首當其衝。<br />\n<br />\n香港人要自保，就要在國際上撇清與中共的關係。最有力的證據，是香港人會追討中共賠償。而白宮聯署要求美國替香港追討中共，就是最確切方法（沒有之一）。這聯署追討成功的機會低，但目的在於&bull;撇&bull;清&bull;關&bull;係！若然聯署失敗，就是最好的證明&mdash;&mdash;證明香港就是中共國。<br />\n<br />\n別人欠你數十億，你卻不追債。為何？大概是因為他是你家人囉。就是同一伙人囉。那麼，別人會怎樣看香港人是何許人呢？<br />\n<br />\n相關影片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=3U_ZCjwYR2w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3U_ZCjwYR2w&d=74s%2FNZguDZpTF4W18ni10HKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=7fc37c66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=3U_ZCjwYR2w</a><br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3125191\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3125191&d=74s%2FNZguDZpTF4W18ni10HKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=5f91f2e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3125191&h=90c9b49a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3125191</a><br />\n<br />\n白宮聯署：<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-reparation-behalf-hong-kong-people-loss-due-chinese-virus?fbclid=IwAR0xVr-tj4q-6EKqhU6N3rft64bZfW5hiooR4TzIp4jERvUA2ZSNsCAhpv8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frequest-reparation-behalf-hong-kong-people-loss-due-chinese-virus%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0xVr-tj4q-6EKqhU6N3rft64bZfW5hiooR4TzIp4jERvUA2ZSNsCAhpv8&d=74s%2FNZguDZpTF4W18ni10HKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=96deaedc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-reparation-behalf-hong-kong-people-loss-due-chinese-virus?fbclid=IwAR0xVr-tj4q-6EKqhU6N3rft64bZfW5hiooR4TzIp4jERvUA2ZSNsCAhpv8</a>"},{"pid":"b23a1389df2a8467c37dd269cb26317dbf181b3c","tid":1975204,"uid":235257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T12:16:29.000Z","msg":"侵：習仔我仲唔打撚死你<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V0oqPUV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV0oqPUV.jpg&h=fafcdfa6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b6e7ea73a6d91fea85724bf3f8ca13b2f003691a","tid":1975204,"uid":235257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T12:34:55.000Z","msg":"簽簽簽"},{"pid":"b79f4191d5300a142e41c899d9b146a813a2aae5","tid":1975204,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T13:26: